<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Choose the plan that fits your needs. Upgrade, downgrade, or cancel anytime. All plans include SSL encryption, GDPR compliance, and automatic backups.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3 class="plan-name">Free</h3>
        <div class="plan-price">
          <span class="currency">₹</span>
          <span class="amount">0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="plan-description">Perfect for individuals getting started</p>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>15 GB Cloud Storage</li>
          <li>2 Email Accounts</li>
          <li>Basic File Sharing</li>
          <li>Web Access</li>
          <li>Community Support</li>
          <li>30-day File Recovery</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-outline">Get Started Free</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div class="popular-badge">Most Popular</div>
        <h3 class="plan-name">Professional</h3>
        <div class="plan-price">
          <span class="currency">₹</span>
          <span class="amount">999</span>
          <span class="period">/month</span>
        </div>
        <p class="plan-description">For professionals and small teams</p>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>1 TB Cloud Storage</li>
          <li>10 Email Accounts (25 GB each)</li>
          <li>Advanced File Sharing & Permissions</li>
          <li>Team Collaboration Tools</li>
          <li>Priority Email Support</li>
          <li>Custom Email Domain</li>
          <li>2-Factor Authentication</li>
          <li>Activity Logs & Monitoring</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Start Free Trial</a>
        <p class="trial-note">14-day free trial, no credit card required</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3 class="plan-name">Business</h3>
        <div class="plan-price">
          <span class="currency">₹</span>
          <span class="amount">2,099</span>
          <span class="period">/user/month</span>
        </div>
        <p class="plan-description">For growing teams and enterprises</p>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Unlimited Cloud Storage</li>
          <li>Unlimited Email Accounts</li>
          <li>Advanced Admin Controls</li>
          <li>Team Management Dashboard</li>
          <li>24/7 Priority Support</li>
          <li>Custom Branding Options</li>
          <li>99.9% Uptime SLA</li>
          <li>Dedicated Account Manager</li>
          <li>Advanced Security Features</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="pricing-note">
      <p>All plans include: SSL encryption, GDPR compliance, automatic backups, and web access. Prices are in INR and exclude 18% GST.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I switch plans later?</h3>
        <p>Yes! You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. Changes take effect immediately and we'll prorate any charges.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you offer refunds?</h3>
        <p>Yes, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all paid plans. If you're not satisfied, contact our support team for a full refund.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
        <p>We accept all major credit/debit cards, UPI, net banking, and digital wallets. Business plans can also pay via invoice.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is there a contract or commitment?</h3>
        <p>No contracts required. All plans are month-to-month and you can cancel anytime without penalty.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What happens when I exceed my storage?</h3>
        <p>You'll receive notifications at 80% and 90% capacity. You can upgrade anytime or purchase additional storage. Your files remain accessible.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you offer discounts for annual billing?</h3>
        <p>Yes! Save 20% when you pay annually. Contact our sales team for custom pricing for larger teams.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Start your free trial today. No credit card required.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary large">Start Free Trial</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline large">Contact Sales</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

